    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Fuuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, E</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You expel a sudden burst of air (approx 25 mph), clearing out dust, smoke, mist and fog as well as extinguishing small fires (such as candles). Diminutive or smaller creatures must make a save to avoid being knocked back 10 ft.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the radius by 5 ft. (up to 30 ft. total).</p>\n\n",
